item.title: Trump Says “Gayle King’s Career Is Over,” Shares Report Claiming ‘CBS Mornings’ Is “Woke”
item.description: “She should have stayed with her belief in TRUMP. She never had the courage to do so. No talent, no ratings, no strength!!!” the president wrote on Truth Social.
